{"tid":2375623,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA與6大洲足協發聲明　不承認球會自組歐洲超級聯賽","createTime":"2021-01-22T07:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T11:55:54.000Z","uid":105567,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c46d03c99d75cddc3b741959f546cc5ae544949e","tid":2375623,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:22:29.000Z","msg":"對於近日有報道，有歐洲頂級球會自組「歐洲超級聯賽」，國際足協（FIFA）聯同亞洲、非洲、中北美洲及加勒比海、南美及歐洲足協發聲明，表示不會承認相關聯賽。 聲明指，任何參加該賽事的球員或球會，將不得參加由國際足協及各大洲足協主辦的任何賽事。 聲明又提到，根據章程，所有比賽應由相關機構舉辦及認可。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-21-2021/69802?fbclid=IwAR1tv31q1cF73dElVjmRkF6I37U0cGkcbgGtqlXUkPI2BRA5iuHf9TdHbWQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-21-2021%2F69802%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1tv31q1cF73dElVjmRkF6I37U0cGkcbgGtqlXUkPI2BRA5iuHf9TdHbWQ&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=3db0f3b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-21-2021/69802?fbclid=IwAR1tv31q1cF73dElVjmRkF6I37U0cGkcbgGtqlXUkPI2BRA5iuHf9TdHbWQ</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2021"},{"pid":"50f316c568754bc7ccf1effce0610e012fc4142f","tid":2375623,"uid":25345,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:25:38.000Z","msg":"歐洲超級聯賽<br />\n係點打法<br />\n一樣打幾廿場定一年只係打十零廿場?<br />\n咁攪法歐聯又點?<br />\n如果打得多,對手咁撚硬,都好傷元氣,冇咩低級隊手hea"},{"pid":"3ea390fd3ebfcb306b3f0578214ff67b4a732474","tid":2375623,"uid":188482,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔參加 到時d頂級球會參加個聯賽自然有大把廣告商落廣告 睇下邊個蝕底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44defc463095f8cc97817a0812745287f38b4dc8","tid":2375623,"uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3ea390fd3ebfcb306b3f0578214ff67b4a732474","tid":2375623,"uid":188482,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"咁咪